21:51.844 --> 21:57.716 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Since the start
of the Arab
uprisings five years ago, we
have seen a tectonic

21:57.750 --> 22:04.089 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
shift across the Middle East and
North Africa,
upending the political order of
the last century.

22:04.123 --> 22:10.496 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
What began with hope has
dissolved into civil
war, extremist violence and
strife. The human

22:10.529 --> 22:16.735 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
toll has been enormous, with
