entire region?

26:09.535 --> 26:11.336 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MADELEINE ALBRIGHT: Well, we do.

26:11.370 --> 26:15.007 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I mean, we were taking about it
this way.
We have to look at the local
aspect of things,

26:15.040 --> 26:19.912 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
because we need to respond to
some of the
changes that are taking place
inside, as Steve

26:19.945 --> 26:24.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
mentioned, but also regionally.
We do have
to look at it regionally and
globally.

26:24.516 --> 26:30.556 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so the countries can help
each other,
and we did discus with them the
possibility

26:30.589 --> 26:34.726 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of kind of looking at some kind
of regional
security agreement, but, at the
same time,

26:34.760 --> 26:38.997 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think we have to recognize the
differences
in the countries.

26:39.031 --> 26:44.369 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Tunisia, quite a different
place, for instance,
from Egypt in terms of how it's
beginning

26:44.403 --> 26:51.009 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to deal with its political
situation and its
economic situation, a good place
to invest.

26:51.043 --> 26:56.114 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Egypt has the problem of being
very large
with a huge unemployed young
population.

26:56.148 --> 27:01.487 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, we have looked at the
specifics in the
countries, but also how they
could be dealt

27:01.520 --> 27:03.422 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
with regionally.

27:03.455 --> 27:06.625 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But doesn't --
Stephen Hadley,
doesn't the security have to
come first, dealing

27:06.658 --> 27:14.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
