it's a repressive
dictator who is -- a civil war,
as you have

27:14.933 --> 27:15.834 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in Syria?

27:15.868 --> 27:17.870 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
STEPHEN HADLEY: Absolutely.

27:17.903 --> 27:23.742 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the message is, there are
green shoots,
we call them, messages of hope
coming out

27:23.775 --> 27:28.914 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the Middle East that need to
be nurtured.
And we need to nurturing them
now, because

27:28.947 --> 27:33.919 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
over the medium and long term,
