an isolated
patch of the Putumayo region in
Colombia's

33:00.011 --> 33:06.151 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
south, where coca leaves are
harvested and
then processes into a coca base,
the foundation

33:06.184 --> 33:07.986 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
