33:08.019 --> 33:13.158 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): Two
acres produces
5,000 or 6,000 grams of coca
base and each

33:13.191 --> 33:16.661 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
