33:16.695 --> 33:21.867 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NADJA DROST: These pickers are
at the bottom
of the rung of Colombia's
multimillion-dollar

33:21.900 --> 33:27.505 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
