34:11.316 --> 34:17.155 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NADJA DROST: That's why, here in
Putumayo,
ground zero of the coca trade,
coca is the

34:17.188 --> 34:19.090 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
