food crops
and been blamed for serious
health problems.

36:03.328 --> 36:08.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, as a part of the expected
peace accords,
both the government and the FARC
have committed

36:08.566 --> 36:14.639 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
