36:14.672 --> 36:18.576 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICARDO, Colombia (through
translator): What's
the fear? That if coca ends,
there will be

36:18.610 --> 36:20.845 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
