36:20.879 --> 36:26.785 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NADJA DROST: And coca base is so
important
to this town, it's even used to
buy goods,

36:26.818 --> 36:33.725 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a valid currency here. The only
