can imagine coca substitution
programs working

36:33.758 --> 36:38.596 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is if the governments invests in
ways to make
alternative crops viable, so
that communities

36:38.630 --> 36:41.099 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
