For the "PBS NewsHour,"
reporting with Bruno
Federico, I'm Nadja Drost in
Putumayo, Colombia.

37:26.711 --> 37:31.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The Colombian
government announced
today that it would soon begin
peace talks

37:31.783 --> 37:37.856 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
with the country's second
