37:45.230 --> 37:59.277 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Next: striking a
balance between
development and conservation to
protect the

37:59.310 --> 38:03.648 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
desert ecosystem of the
