has the story.

38:06.718 --> 38:14.592 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: The views from Chino
Canyon high
above Palm Springs are grand.
The rocky hillsides

38:14.626 --> 38:20.398 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
are home to the endangered
Peninsular bighorn
sheep and a number of other
species. But this

38:20.431 --> 38:24.202 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
tranquil canyon has long been an
environmental
battleground.

38:24.235 --> 38:28.473 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICKIE MCLAUGHLIN, Activist: If
the project
had been completed, you would
have been looking

38:28.506 --> 38:35.246 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
