resort, and
all surrounded by an 18-hole
golf course.

38:35.280 --> 38:40.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: Nickie McLaughlin
heads up a local
nonprofit that recently
purchased 600 acres

38:40.919 --> 38:44.956 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of privately owned land in the
canyon to prevent
that development.

38:44.989 --> 38:49.561 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICKIE MCLAUGHLIN: There will be
nothing here.
