perpetuity.

38:49.594 --> 38:51.429 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
This was a huge success.

38:51.462 --> 38:56.301 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: The push to save Chino
Canyon is
part of a much larger
environmental conservation

38:56.334 --> 39:02.840 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
effort unfolding in Coachella
Valley, a 45-mile
stretch of desert dotted with
upscale cities

39:02.874 --> 39:07.111 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
