areas of deep
poverty.

39:07.145 --> 39:12.417 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The population here is expected
to almost
double in the next 20 years.
Golf courses

39:12.450 --> 39:15.453 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and condos butt up against
fragile desert
ecosystems.

39:15.486 --> 39:18.323 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TOM KIRK, Coachella Valley
Association of
Governments: In a lot of places
throughout

39:18.356 --> 39:26.130 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
this country, we know that we
have done development
perhaps in a rash and vast way.
In the Coachella

39:26.164 --> 39:27.932 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Valley, we didn't want to do
that.

39:27.966 --> 39:32.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: Tom Kirk heads up the
local government
agency now managing a plan that
took more

39:32.470 --> 39:39.177 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
than 10 years to develop and
that will be
on the books 75 years into the
future.

39:39.210 --> 39:45.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's called the Coachella Valley
Multiple
Species Habitat Conservation
Plan. Nearly

39:45.049 --> 39:51.055 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
2,000-pages long, it is
essentially a huge
compromise between government
agencies, private

39:51.089 --> 39:55.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
landowners and developers,
scientists, and
environmental groups.

39:55.260 --> 39:57.295 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
How did you bring everyone
together?

39:57.328 --> 40:02.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TOM KIRK: They were brought
together perhaps
not by choice, but by need.
Before there was

40:03.001 --> 40:07.939 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
