evaluated on its
own. It would take a lot of
time. There'd

40:07.972 --> 40:14.545 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
be a lot of uncertainty. Today,
instead of
dealing with every project
individually, we

40:14.579 --> 40:17.115 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
look at a million acres at the
same time.

40:17.148 --> 40:22.987 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: Kirk, who brought us
to a now preserved
area called Whitewater Canyon
that had been

40:23.021 --> 40:27.458 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
