me how the
habitat plan works.

40:27.492 --> 40:32.330 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TOM KIRK: You can actually
develop anywhere
in the plan, but it is very
difficult to do

40:32.363 --> 40:37.602 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
so in conservation areas, and
very easy to
do so, relatively, on the valley
floor.

40:37.635 --> 40:43.207 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: Out of the million or
so acres in
the valley, 700,000 have been
designated as

40:43.241 --> 40:49.414 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
