forward in a timely
manner because the necessary
endangered species

40:55.353 --> 40:58.089 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
permits have already been
secured.

40:58.122 --> 41:04.262 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The plan is designed to ensure
the survival
of 27 endangered and threatened
species, large

41:04.295 --> 41:10.368 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and small animals, rare plants,
and one little
desert dweller well known in
these parts,

41:10.401 --> 41:12.203 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
