41:12.236 --> 41:17.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAMERON BARROWS, Ecologist:
Here's a little
baby fringe-toed lizard, just
hatched probably

41:17.975 --> 41:19.911 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
