41:19.944 --> 41:23.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: I met up with one of
the few people
who has a special permit to
catch this endangered

41:23.848 --> 41:29.587 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
